== 制作 ==

=== 编剧和早期发展 ===
编剧蒂莫西·哈里斯（{{lang|en|Timothy Harris}}）在20世纪80年代初经常和两兄弟打网球，两人既有钱又节俭，经常打赌或相互竞争。某天打球这两兄弟又发生冲突，哈里斯的心情大受影响，回到家后认定这两人实在不怎么样，但也给予他灵感，设想两兄弟打赌先天与后天因素对人的能力影响有多大。哈里斯把构想告诉经常合作编剧的赫舍尔·魏因格罗德（{{lang|en|Herschel Weingrod}}），后者觉得靠谱。哈里斯还从亲身经历汲取灵感，他曾是[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]][[费尔法克斯大道|费尔法克斯大道]]（{{lang|en|Fairfax Avenue}}）附近的破落户，这里“犯罪丛生，每个人要么曾面对枪口，要么曾被强奸”。<ref name="BIOralHistory" />

哈里斯与魏因格罗德研究[[日用品|日用品]]交易市场<ref name="BIOralHistory" />，了解金融市场重大事件，如苏联企图操纵小麦市场，亨特兄弟试图操纵白银市场，引发[[白銀星期四|白銀星期四]]等。片中的交易商品是橙汁和猪肚，因为两位编剧觉得公众根本想不到如此平凡的东西也会在期货市场交易，所以会更加好笑。<ref name="NPRHistory">{{cite web | url = https://www.npr.org/sections/money/2013/07/24/205167911/guy-who-wrote-trading-places-responds-to-our-show-about-his-movie?t=1593777466393 | title = Guy Who Wrote 'Trading Places' Responds To Our Show About His Movie | date = 2013-07-24 | publisher = [[全国公共广播电台|NPR]] | accessdate = 2020-11-11 | archiveurl = http://web.archive.org/web/20201019211025/https://www.npr.org/sections/money/2013/07/24/205167911/guy-who-wrote-trading-places-responds-to-our-show-about-his-movie | archivedate = 2020-10-19 | deadurl = no}}</ref>为了解[[交易大厅|交易大厅]]运作，哈里斯咨询商品交易从业人士。两位编剧认为，只要内容不致局限在金融市场本身，选择商品交易市场充当电影背景应该会很有趣。为吸引观众，他们决定把故事背景放在费城，因为这里是美国的诞生地，代表美国梦、理想主义和对幸福的追求。如此情境下，黑人比利·瓦沦丁沿街乞讨就形成鲜明对比。<ref name="BIOralHistory" />编剧知道部分观众可能很难理解两位男主角最终是如何赢得大笔金钱，但希望大家届时只为成功感到兴奋，不去在意这些细节<ref name="NPRHistory" />。

编剧把剧本以《黑与白》（{{lang|en|''Black and White''}}）之名卖予[[派拉蒙影業|派拉蒙影業]]，公司高管[[杰弗瑞·卡森伯格|杰弗瑞·卡森伯格]]邀请导演[[約翰·蘭迪斯|約翰·蘭迪斯]]接手。兰迪斯对剧本名称不以为然，<ref name="BIOralHistory" />但觉得内容不错，可与20世纪30年代导演[[法蘭克·卡普拉|法蘭克·卡普拉]]、[[李歐·麥卡瑞|李歐·麥卡瑞]]及[[普莱斯顿·斯特奇斯|普莱斯顿·斯特奇斯]]（{{lang|en|Preston Sturges}}）经常讽刺社会结构、阶层及文化议题的[[脱线喜剧|脱线喜剧]]媲美。兰迪斯希望本片反映20世纪80年代的上述内容<ref name="BIOralHistory" /><ref name="EmpireRetrospective">{{cite journal | first = Nick | last = de Semlyen | url = https://www.empireonline.com/movies/features/80s-heroes-john-landis/ | title = '80s heroes: John Landis | date = 2016-05-26 | journal = [[帝國雜誌|Empire]]  | accessdate = 2020-11-11 | archivedate = 2020-09-07 | archiveurl = http://web.archive.org/web/20200907050142/https://www.empireonline.com/movies/features/80s-heroes-john-landis/ | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref name="WAPOLandisInterview">{{cite news | first = Geoff | last = Edgers | url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/arts-and-entertainment/wp/2015/10/15/not-just-bill-cosby-eddie-murphy-also-didnt-want-to-play-stevie-wonder-at-snl-40/ | title = Not just Bill Cosby: Eddie Murphy also didn't want to play Stevie Wonder at 'SNL 40' | date = 2015-10-15 | newspaper = The Washington Post | accessdate = 2020-11-11 | archiveurl = http://web.archive.org/web/20200712063926/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/arts-and-entertainment/wp/2015/10/15/not-just-bill-cosby-eddie-murphy-also-didnt-want-to-play-stevie-wonder-at-snl-40/ | archivedate = 2020-07-12 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，还称80年代和30年代相比也没多大区别，多出来的基本上就是脏话和裸体<ref name="EmpireRetrospective" />。导演还表示，他也花费不少时间才理解片尾的交易到底是怎么回事儿<ref name="BIOralHistory" />。

=== 选角 ===
[[File:Dan_Aykroyd_cropped.jpg|thumb]]觉得[[丹·艾克洛德|丹·艾克洛德]]（图，摄于2009年）此前的成功应当归功于已故演员[[約翰·貝魯西|約翰·貝魯西]]，所以不想找他扮演男主角。但导演[[約翰·蘭迪斯|約翰·蘭迪斯]]曾与艾克洛德合作，决定请他出演]]

哈里斯和魏因格罗德编剧时的构想是请喜剧双人组合[[李察·普瑞爾|李察·普瑞爾]]和[[吉恩·怀尔德|吉恩·怀尔德]]分别饰演瓦伦汀和温索普<ref name="BIOralHistory" /><ref name="EmpireRetrospective" />，两人因《[[油腔滑调|油腔滑调]]》（''{{lang|en|Stir Crazy}}''，1980年）大获成功变得炙手可热<ref name="IndieWireTidbits" />。普瑞爾在吸毒时烧成重伤，制片商决定另请高明<ref name="BIOralHistory" /><ref name="WAPOFreebasing">{{cite news | first = Elahe | last = Izadi | url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/arts-and-entertainment/wp/2016/08/30/remembering-gene-wilder-and-richard-pryor-a-magical-and-complicated-comedy-duo/ | title = Remembering Gene Wilder and Richard Pryor, a magical and complicated comedy duo | date = 2016-08-30 | newspaper = The Washington Post | accessdate = 2020-11-11 | archiveurl = http://web.archive.org/web/20200710090246/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/arts-and-entertainment/wp/2016/08/30/remembering-gene-wilder-and-richard-pryor-a-magical-and-complicated-comedy-duo/ | archivedate = 2020-07-10 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。派拉蒙影业建议邀请艾迪·墨菲<ref name="BIOralHistory" />。公司起初对墨菲在处女作《[[48小時|48小時]]》（1983年，此时还没上映）中的表现不满意，该片一开始也打算请普瑞爾主演<ref name="ChicagoTribuneApril71985">{{cite news | first = Larry | last = Kart | url = https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-1985-04-07-8501190904-story.html | title = Eddie Murphy: Comedy's Supernova Sends Humor Into A Different | date = 1985-04-07 | newspaper = [[芝加哥論壇報|Chicago Tribune]] | accessdate = 2020-11-11 | archiveurl = http://archive.vn/WX9XE | archivedate = 2020-07-07 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。但电影试映观众反响热烈，促使派拉蒙改变主意<ref name="BIOralHistory" /><ref name="EmpireRetrospective" />。墨菲凭在《周六夜现场》演出声名鹊起，兰迪斯虽然没听说过，但对墨菲的试镜带很满意，亲赴纽约与他面谈<ref name="BIOralHistory" />。墨菲自称参演《颠倒乾坤》的片酬是35万美元<ref name="WashingtonPost350K">{{cite news | first = Chuck | archivedate = 2020-08-18 | deadurl = no | last = Conconi | url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/lifestyle/1987/03/18/personalities/aee2a24f-3067-40ff-ba57-6f7ec685e7fb/   | title = Personalities | date = 1987-03-18 | newspaper = The Washington Post | accessdate = 2020-11-11 | archiveurl = http://web.archive.org/web/20200818112531/https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/lifestyle/1987/03/18/personalities/aee2a24f-3067-40ff-ba57-6f7ec685e7fb/}}</ref>，但有报导称实际数字高达100万<ref name="WashingtonPost1Million">{{cite news | first = Gary | last = Arnold | url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/lifestyle/style/1983/07/31/murphy-38/e3f17cb9-546e-4115-8707-3f7dd76733e8/ | title = Murphy & | date = 1983-07-31 | newspaper = The Washington Post | accessdate = 2020-11-11 | archiveurl = http://web.archive.org/web/20200818115236/https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/lifestyle/style/1983/07/31/murphy-38/e3f17cb9-546e-4115-8707-3f7dd76733e8/ | archivedate = 2020-08-18 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

兰迪斯想请艾克洛德和墨菲共同主演，他和艾克洛德在音乐喜剧片《[[福祿雙霸天|福祿雙霸天]]》（1980年）的合作十分愉快。兰迪斯称：“他能轻松演好（温索普）……说明你想要的效果，他就能做到，我觉得他会很出色。”派拉蒙影业对艾克洛德观感普遍，公司高管认为他与[[約翰·貝魯西|約翰·貝魯西]]组合时表现更好，但貝魯西已经去世，艾克洛德独立演出时表现一般，而且近来几部电影票房不佳。最终艾克洛德同意削减片酬。<ref name="BIOralHistory" />

制片商反对邀请杰米·李·柯蒂斯主演。柯蒂斯此时尚属“[[尖叫女王_(電影術語)|尖叫女王]]”，大部分演出经验都是低档[[B級片|B級片]]。她曾与兰迪斯在恐怖纪录片《[[即将上映|即将上映]]》（''{{lang|en|Coming Soon}}''）合作，饰演节目主持人。柯蒂斯觉得一直只演恐怖片会限制未来职业前景，想拓宽戏路。她的母亲[[珍妮特·利|珍妮特·利]]因出演《[[驚魂記|驚魂記]]》扬名，但她为摆脱恐怖片宁愿谢绝参演《[[惊魂记2|惊魂记2]]》（''{{lang|en|Psycho II}}''，1983年）。<ref name="BIOralHistory" />柯蒂斯不久前出于人情主演[[約翰·卡本特|約翰·卡本特]]执导、[[黛布拉·希尔|黛布拉·希尔]]（{{lang|en|Debra Hill}}）制片的[[砍杀电影|砍杀电影]]《[[月光光心慌慌2|月光光心慌慌2]]》，片酬达100万美元，但演出《颠倒乾坤》的酬劳仅七万美元。<ref name="BIOralHistory" />面对是否研究如何演妓女的问题柯蒂斯笑称：“我也想说去过[[42街_(曼哈頓)|42街]]（红灯区）接客，但我真没有啊。”<ref name="PeopleCurtis">{{cite journal | first = Carol | last = Wallace | url = https://people.com/archive/beware-soft-shoulders-jamie-lee-curtis-career-has-changed-course-vol-20-no-8/ | title = Beware: Soft Shoulders—Jamie Lee Curtis' Career Has Changed Course | date = 1983-08-22 | journal = People | accessdate = 2020-11-12 | archiveurl = http://web.archive.org/web/20200705134358/https://people.com/archive/beware-soft-shoulders-jamie-lee-curtis-career-has-changed-course-vol-20-no-8/ | archivedate = 2020-07-05 | deadurl = no}}</ref>获选出演时她本是一头长发，但在服装设计师[[戴博拉·纳杜尔曼|戴博拉·纳杜尔曼]]（{{lang|en|Deborah Nadoolman}}）建议下剪短<ref name="EmpireRetrospective" />。

拉尔夫·贝拉米是出演伦道夫·杜克的第一人选<ref name="IndieWireTidbits" />。兰迪斯想请20世纪30到40年代比较有名，同时又没演过大坏蛋的演员诠释莫蒂默·杜克，他的第一人选是[[雷·米倫|雷·米倫]]，但米倫身体状况不佳，保险公司经检查后拒绝为他参演本片承保。导演在电影即将开拍之际想到唐·阿米契，但选角总监居然宣称阿米契已经过世。<ref name="EmpireRetrospective" />兰迪斯对此颇感难以致信并与[[美国演员公会|美国演员公会]]联系，想知道他的下落。公会确认阿米契没有经纪人，版税收入都是转交给他身在[[亚利桑那州|亚利桑那州]]的儿子，兰迪斯至此相信阿米契真的死了。得知兰迪斯在找阿米契后，派拉蒙影业工作人员自称经常在加利福尼亚州[[圣莫尼卡|圣莫尼卡]]的[[圣维森特大道|圣维森特大道]]（{{lang|en|San Vicente Boulevard}}）看到阿米契，导演于是联系[[查号台|查号台]]寻找。<ref name="BIOralHistory" />阿米契已经十余年没有参加电影演出，自称这是因为没人请他出演<ref name="BIOralHistory" /><ref name="NYTImesJune171983">{{cite news | first = Chris | last = Chase | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1983/06/17/movies/at-the-movies-their-credits-include-a-mad-computer.html?searchResultPosition=9 | title = At The Movies; Their credits include a mad computer. | date = 1983-06-17 | newspaper = The New York Times | accessdate = 2020-11-12 | archivedate = 2020-11-07 | deadurl = no | page = C10 | archiveurl = http://web.archive.org/web/20201107173454/https://www.nytimes.com/1983/06/17/movies/at-the-movies-their-credits-include-a-mad-computer.html}}</ref>。制片商觉得不值得花费米倫同等片酬请阿米契演出，阿米契此时经济富足，根本不怕失去工作机会，所以坚持要同工同酬<ref name="ChicagoTribuneAmechePay">{{cite news | first = Richard | last = Christiansen | url = https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-1988-10-23-8802100003-story.html | title = Forever Ameche | date = 1988-10-23 | newspaper = Chicago Tribune | accessdate = 2020-11-12 | archiveurl = http://archive.is/tT7rR | archivedate = 2020-07-07 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref name="PeopleAmeche">{{cite journal | first = Richard | last = Sanders | url = https://people.com/archive/in-the-sleeper-of-the-summer-cocoons-don-ameche-catches-hollywoods-younger-sex-symbols-napping-vol-23-no-10/ | title = In the Sleeper of the Summer, Cocoon's Don Ameche Catches Hollywood's Younger Sex Symbols Napping | date = 1985-09-02 | journal = People | accessdate = 2020-11-12 | archiveurl = http://web.archive.org/web/20200707043738/https://people.com/archive/in-the-sleeper-of-the-summer-cocoons-don-ameche-catches-hollywoods-younger-sex-symbols-napping-vol-23-no-10/ | archivedate = 2020-07-07 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。兰迪斯声称派拉蒙对邀请长期远离银幕的阿米契演出不满，所以削减本片预算<ref name="EmpireRetrospective" />。

[[约翰·吉尔古德|约翰·吉尔古德]]和[[罗尼·巴克|罗尼·巴克]]（{{lang|en|Ronnie Barker}}）都曾是温索普管家科尔曼的扮演人选，但巴克拒绝在离家（他家在英国）超过11公里的地方参与电影摄制<ref name="IndieWireTidbits" /><ref name="EmpireRetrospective" />。[[水门事件|水门事件]]核心人物[[戈登·利迪|戈登·利迪]]（{{lang|en|G. Gordon Liddy}}）获邀出演贪腐官员克拉伦斯·比克斯，起初他很有兴趣，但在得知片中比克斯沦为大猖猖的情侣后谢绝，保罗·格里森接手。片中比克斯乘火车时看书打发时间，这本书便是利迪的自传。<ref name="IndieWireTidbits" />唐·麦克劳德因在[[新秀麗|新秀麗]]旗下品牌[[美国旅行者|美国旅行者]]的广告中扮演大猩猩闻名，并因此获聘出演包括本片在内的多部电影<ref name="DonMcLeod1" /><ref name="DonMcLeod2" />。

