《颠倒乾坤》的配乐由[[埃尔默·伯恩斯坦|埃尔默·伯恩斯坦]]作曲<ref name="MusicClassicFm">{{cite web | deadurl = no | url = https://www.classicfm.com/composers/mozart/pictures/mozarts-music-movies/mozart-music-movie-trading-place/ | website = Classic FM | accessdate = 2020-11-12 | title = Trading Place -3. Trading Place | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200921013324/https://www.classicfm.com/composers/mozart/pictures/mozarts-music-movies/mozart-music-movie-trading-place/ | archivedate = 2020-09-21}}</ref>，他已多次和兰迪斯合作，如《福祿雙霸天》和恐怖喜剧片《[[美国狼人在伦敦|美国狼人在伦敦]]》（''{{lang|en|An American Werewolf in London}}''，1981年）<ref name="MusicRoyalAbertHall">{{cite web | title = Celebrate Hollywood legend Elmer Bernstein with a magnificent new show | url = https://www.royalalberthall.com/about-the-hall/news/2016/november/celebrate-hollywood-legend-elmer-bernstein-with-a-magnificent-new-show/ | publisher = [[皇家阿爾伯特音樂廳|Royal Albert Hall]] | date = 2016-11-03 | accessdate = 2020-11-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200809143714/https://www.royalalberthall.com/about-the-hall/news/2016/november/celebrate-hollywood-legend-elmer-bernstein-with-a-magnificent-new-show/ | archivedate = 2020-08-09 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。采用[[沃尔夫冈·阿马德乌斯·莫扎特|沃尔夫冈·阿马德乌斯·莫扎特]][[喜歌剧|喜歌剧]]《[[费加罗的婚礼|费加罗的婚礼]]》作为配乐基本主题源自兰迪斯的构想，此前他导演的电影就用古典音乐代表上层阶级，他觉得这应该也适合金融行业举足轻重的精英人士<ref name="MusicFilmTracks">{{cite web | title = Trading Places | archivedate = 2020-08-09 | deadurl = no | url = https://www.filmtracks.com/titles/trading_places.html | website = Filmtracks.com | date = 2011-12-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200809152306/https://www.filmtracks.com/titles/trading_places.html | accessdate = 2020-11-12}}</ref><ref name="MusicBernsteincom">{{cite news | first = Jon | last = Burlingame | title = Hollywood's Score Keeper | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-2001-nov-08-ca-1557-story.html | newspaper = Los Angeles Times | date = 2001-11-08 | accessdate = 2020-11-12 | archivedate = 2020-08-09 | deadurl = no | arc