== 发行 ==
{{see also|1983年电影}}
业界预计1983年夏（六至九月）能打破前一年14亿美元的暑期票房纪录，有望大卖的电影包括《[[星際大戰|星球大战]]》三部曲之三《[[星際大戰六部曲：絕地大反攻|绝地归来]]》、《[[超人III|超人III]]》，以及最新的[[詹姆斯·邦德系列电影|詹姆斯·邦德系列电影]]《[[鐵金剛勇破爆炸黨|鐵金剛勇破爆炸黨]]》，计划在这短短16周内上映的电影超过40部。片商只能想办设法避免自家电影碰上太过强劲的对手，影响票房收入。<ref name="NYTimesHwoodForecast">{{cite news | first = Aljean | last = Harmetz | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1983/05/16/movies/hollywood-forecast-best-summer-at-box-office.html | title = Hollywood Forecast: Best Summer At Box Office | date = 1983-05-16 | newspaper = The New York Times | accessdate = 2020-11-12 | archivedate = 2020-08-28 | deadurl = no | page = C15 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200828232705/https://www.nytimes.com/1983/05/16/movies/hollywood-forecast-best-summer-at-box-office.html}}</ref>派拉蒙影业选择在暑期刚开始时发行《颠倒乾坤》，这样电影就能在这繁忙的几个月上映更长时间，更有望取得好成绩。此时的市场大片都是科幻和[[超级英雄|超级英雄]]题材，喜剧片已属冷门类型，目标观众就是已经看过大片或对大片没兴趣的消费者。《绝地归来》在五月上映，《超人III》六月中旬发行，《颠倒乾坤》夹在两者中间。续集通常凭借前作的口碑卖座希望很大，但片商对《颠倒乾坤》也很有信心，觉得几位演员的号召力足以保证成功。<ref name="NYTimesHwoodForecast" />

=== 票房 ===
1983年6月8日，《颠倒乾坤》在北美1375家电影院全面上映<ref name="NYTimesReleaseDate">{{cite news | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1984/02/17/obituaries/avon-long-actor-and-singer-in-theater-and-film-50-years.html | title = Akyroyd In 'Trading Places' | date = 1983-06-08 | newspaper = The New York Times | first = Janet | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200705233030/https://www.nytimes.com/1984/02/17/obituaries/avon-long-actor-and-singer-in-theater-and-film-50-years.html | archivedate = 2020-07-05 | deadurl = no | last = Maslin | page = B4 | accessdate = 2020-11-13}}</ref><ref name="TheNumbersSummary">{{cite web | title = Trading Places (1983) | url = https://www.the-numbers.com/movie/Trading-Places#tab=summary | website = The Numbers | accessdate = 2020-11-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200809151436/https://www.the-numbers.com/movie/Trading-Places | archivedate = 2020-08-09 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，前两天收入170万美元，周末又进账730万美元，平均每家电影院5344美元，周末票房在所有电影中排第三，仅次于发行第三周的《绝地归来》（1200万美元）和同一周上映的《鐵金剛勇破爆炸黨》（890万美元）<ref name="TheNumbersWeekendJune10">{{cite web | title = Weekend Domestic Chart for June 10, 1983 | url = https://www.the-numbers.com/box-office-chart/weekend/1983/06/10 | website = The Numbers | accessdate = 2020-11-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200809115015/https://www.the-numbers.com/box-office-chart/weekend/1983/06/10 | archivedate = 2020-08-09 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。影片第二个周末拿下700万美元，仅次于《绝地归来》（1120万美元）和刚刚上映的《超人III》（1330万美元）同样排名第三<ref name="TheNumbersWeekendJune17">{{cite web | title = Weekend Domestic Chart for June 17, 1983 | url = https://www.the-numbers.com/box-office-chart/weekend/1983/06/17 | website = The Numbers | accessdate = 2020-11-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200809125840/https://www.the-numbers.com/box-office-chart/weekend/1983/06/17 | archivedate = 2020-08-09 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。电影第三个周末收入550万美元位居第五，落后于《绝地归来》（1110万美元）、《超人III》（900万美元）、新上映的性喜剧《[[留校查看2|留校查看2]]》（''{{lang|en|Porky's II: The Next Day}}''，700万美元）和科幻恐怖片《[[阴阳魔界_(1983年电影)|阴阳魔界]]》（''{{lang|en|Twilight Zone: The Movie}}''，660万美元）<ref name="TheNumbersWeekendJune24">{{cite web | title = Weekend Domestic Chart for June 24, 1983 | url = https://www.the-numbers.com/box-office-chart/weekend/1983/06/24 | website = The Numbers | accessdate = 2020-11-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200809170712/https://www.the-numbers.com/box-office-chart/weekend/1983/06/24 | archivedate = 2020-08-09 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

《颠倒乾坤》始终没有在票房榜登顶，但却保持前十连续17周之久<ref name="TheNumbersWeekeends">{{cite web | title = Trading Places (1983) | url = https://www.the-numbers.com/movie/Trading-Places#tab=box-office | website = The Numbers | accessdate = 2020-11-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200809151436/https://www.the-numbers.com/movie/Trading-Places | archivedate = 2020-08-09 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。截至九月，影片已累积进账8060万美元<ref name="NYTimesRecordSummer">{{cite news | page = 168 | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1983/09/11/movies/jedi-leads-record-setting-summer-film-season.html | title = 'Jedi' Leads Record-setting Summer Film Season | date = 1983-09-11 | newspaper = The New York Times | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | accessdate = 2020-11-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200704164359/https://www.nytimes.com/1983/09/11/movies/jedi-leads-record-setting-summer-film-season.html | archivedate = 2020-07-04 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。电影的院线发行总票房约为9040万美元<ref name="TheNumbersSummary" />，在1983年电影票房榜上位居第四，仅次于《绝地归来》（3.09亿美元）、《[[親密關係_(電影)|母女情深]]》（1.08亿美元），以及派拉蒙影业的意外惊喜《[[闪电舞|闪电舞]]》（''{{lang|en|Flashdance}}''，9046万美元）<ref name="NYTimesRecordSummer" /><ref name="TheNumbers1983">{{cite web | title = Top 1983 Movies at the Domestic Box Office | url = https://www.the-numbers.com/box-office-records/domestic/all-movies/cumulative/released-in-1983 | website = [[The_Numbers|The Numbers]] | accessdate = 2020-11-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200809213409/https://www.the-numbers.com/box-office-records/domestic/all-movies/cumulative/released-in-1983 | archivedate = 2020-08-09 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。业界专家于1997年估计，制片方因本片获得的总收入为4060万美元<ref name="VarietyRentals">{{cite journal | title = Rental champs: Rate of return | url = https://variety.com/1997/digital/features/rental-champs-rate-of-return-1116680329/ | date = 1997-12-15 | journal = Variety | accessdate = 2020-11-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201024043302/https://variety.com/1997/digital/features/rental-champs-rate-of-return-1116680329/ | archivedate = 2020-10-24 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。《颠倒乾坤》在其他国家的票房表现缺乏记载<ref name="TheNumbersSummary" /><ref name="BOMOverview">{{cite web | title = Trading Places (1983) | url = https://www.boxofficemojo.com/title/tt0086465/?ref_=bo_rl_ti | website = [[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] | accessdate = 2020-11-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200809164207/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/title/tt0086465/?ref_=bo_rl_ti | archivedate = 2020-08-09 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

== 反响 ==

=== 专业评价 ===
[[File:Jamie_Lee_Curtis_(28770868877)_(cropped).jpg|thumb]]（摄于2018年）不过是恐怖片女星，对她不屑一顾，但她在《颠倒乾坤》中的突破演出广受好评]]

《颠倒乾坤》赢得评论界普遍好评<ref name="BIOralHistory" />，影评人将电影与20世纪30至40年代凸显社会意识的喜剧片相提并论，如《[[我的戈弗雷|我的戈弗雷]]》（''{{lang|en|My Man Godfrey}}''，1936年）、《[[轻松生活_(1937年电影)|轻松生活]]》（''{{lang|en|Easy Living}}''，1937年）、《[[七月圣诞|七月圣诞]]》（''{{lang|en|Christmas in July}}''，1940年）和《[[蘇利文遊記|蘇利文遊記]]》等普莱斯顿·斯特奇斯、弗兰克·卡普拉及[[格雷戈里·拉·卡瓦|格雷戈里·拉·卡瓦]]（{{lang|en|Gregory La Cava}}）导演的作品<ref name="NYTimesReleaseDate" /><ref name="ReviewCanby">{{cite web | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1983/06/19/movies/film-view-trading-places-brings-30-s-comedy-into-the-80-s.html | title = Film View; 'trading Places' Brings 30's Comedy Into The 80's | date = 1983-06-19 | newspaper = The New York Times | accessdate = 2020-11-12 | first = Vincent | last = Canby | archivedate = 2020-11-08 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201108032709/https://www.nytimes.com/1983/06/19/movies/film-view-trading-places-brings-30-s-comedy-into-the-80-s.html | page = 223}}</ref><ref name="ReviewEBERT">{{cite web | first = Roger | last = Ebert | authorlink = 罗杰·伊伯特 | title = Trading Places | accessdate = 2020-11-12 | archivedate = 2020-09-26 | url = https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/trading-places-1983 | website = RogerEbert.com | date = 1983-06-08 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200926193851/https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/trading-places-1983 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref name="ReviewWapoArnold">{{cite news | first = Gary | last = Arnold | title = The Ups & | url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/lifestyle/1983/06/08/the-ups-38/5c6cf5d7-e887-4d6f-b985-69ebd7060300/  | newspaper = The Washington Post | date = 1983-06-08 | accessdate = 2020-11-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200930081847/https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/lifestyle/1983/06/08/the-ups-38/5c6cf5d7-e887-4d6f-b985-69ebd7060300/ | archivedate = 2020-09-30 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。[[珍妮特·马斯林|珍妮特·马斯林]]（{{lang|en|Janet Maslin}}）在《纽约时报》发文，称本片颇为讨喜但“亏欠”脱线喜剧良多：“如果普莱斯顿·斯特奇斯灵感少一点的同时又拥有大笔资金，他十有八九会拍类似《颠倒乾坤》的电影”，意指影片创意与斯特奇斯的作品相当尚有不及<ref name="NYTimesReleaseDate" />。《[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]》刊登加里·阿诺德（{{lang|en|Gary Arnold}}）的文章，称本片与30到40年代的老片相比矛盾之处太多<ref name="ReviewWapoArnold" />。[[文森特·坎比|文森特·坎比]]（{{lang|en|Vincent Canby}}）感觉本片就像20世纪80年代时髦版的脱线喜剧，只是过去这类电影通常强调“钱不重要”的道德观，但《颠倒乾坤》没有这种意味，人物没有对金融系统下手或暴露腐败，最后的行动只是报复杜克兄弟顺便大发横财。不过坎比仍然认为本片是很长一段时间以来难得的美国喜剧杰作。<ref name="ReviewCanby" />马斯林也觉得电影过于沉迷财富，无意批评金融体系及其失败之处。在她看来，这就像电影形式的[[美国梦|美国梦]]。<ref name="NYTimesReleaseDate" />

《[[芝加哥读者报|芝加哥读者报]]》（{{lang|en|''Chicago Reader''}}）的[[戴夫·基尔|戴夫·基尔]]（{{lang|en|Dave Kehr}}）称，《颠倒乾坤》在向脱线喜剧致敬，但只保留“最令观众满意的环节”，其他特点全部剥离，避免深入该类型常见的道德冲突<ref name="ReviewDaveKehr">{{cite news | first = Dave | last = Kehr | archivedate = 2020-09-30 | deadurl = no | url = https://www.chicagoreader.com/chicago/trading-places/Film?oid=2960467 | title = Trading Places | date = 1983 | newspaper = Chicago Reader | accessdate = 2020-11-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200930081910/https://www.chicagoreader.com/chicago/trading-places/Film?oid=2960467}}</ref>。《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|综艺]]》杂志刊登的评论认为，电影中段幽默尚显不足<ref name="ReviewVariety" />。《[[人物_(雜誌)|人物]]》周刊称赞影片结局完美，但阿诺德觉得部分观众可能不明白“英雄”最后到底有何做为，这样安排太过依赖观众对“英雄”及其行为的理解<ref name="ReviewWapoArnold" /><ref name="ReviewPeople">{{cite journal | title = Picks and Pans Review: Trading Places | url = https://people.com/archive/picks-and-pans-review-trading-places-vol-19-no-25/ | journal = People | date = 1983-06-27 | accessdate = 2020-11-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201007121212/https://people.com/archive/picks-and-pans-review-trading-places-vol-19-no-25/ | archivedate = 2020-10-07 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。在他看来，即便是从滑稽电影角度出发，影片情节也太过天马行空<ref name="ReviewWapoArnold" />。[[罗杰·伊伯特|罗杰·伊伯特]]称，本片结局没有“疯狂的追逐”，这就已经很有创意<ref name="ReviewEBERT" />。他认可电影在表现温索普和瓦伦丁社会地位互换时既不依赖明显的种族戏剧冲突，也没落入情景喜剧的俗套。伊伯特赞扬片中着重体现人物发展，以鲜明的人物特点令电影更加生动有趣。在他看来，这令本片剧本更具深度，不像大部分喜剧片那样流于肤浅。<ref name="ReviewEBERT" />

演员表现同样普受好评<ref name="ReviewVariety" /><ref name="NYTimesReleaseDate" /><ref name="ReviewEBERT" />。马斯林认为影片选角颇显怪异但效果很好，融多个好莱坞世代于一身<ref name="NYTimesReleaseDate" />。伊伯特认为演员和编剧表现出色，令原本可能局限于思维定势的人物升华，艾克洛德和墨菲堪称黄金搭档<ref name="ReviewEBERT" />。坎比声称，墨菲的表现足够说明他何以成为十年来最成功的笑匠<ref name="ReviewCanby" />。影评人把瓦伦丁和他在《48小时》中的角色对比<ref name="ReviewWaPOKempley">{{cite news | first = Rita | last = Kempley | title = 'Trading Places': Right On The Money | newspaper = The Washington Post | date = 1983-06-10 | accessdate = 2020-08-18 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200818112154/https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/lifestyle/1983/06/10/trading-places-right-on-the-money/703b47e4-9883-458c-abb5-ef023056fe72/ | archivedate = 2020-08-18 | url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/lifestyle/1983/06/10/trading-places-right-on-the-money/703b47e4-9883-458c-abb5-ef023056fe72/}}</ref><ref name="ReviewWapoArnold" />。阿诺德称本片证明墨菲的成功绝非侥幸，他的喜剧才华实在来劲儿<ref name="ReviewWapoArnold" />。坎比认为墨菲通过《颠倒乾坤》证明他“轻盈、优雅同时又能掌控热闹场面”的表演功底<ref name="ReviewCanby" />。

影评人普遍认为艾克洛德表现优于之前出演的电影<ref name="ReviewCanby" /><ref name="ReviewWapoArnold" />。《人物》周刊声称，哪怕观众已因失败作《[[臭味相投|臭味相投]]》（''{{lang|en|Neighbors}}''，1981年）和《[[双面博士_(1983年电影)|双面博士]]》（''{{lang|en|Doctor Detroit}}''）放弃艾克洛德，《颠倒乾坤》 也能重振他的事业<ref name="ReviewPeople" />。坎比称赞艾克洛德的表现比过去更稳定，证明他不是依靠与約翰·貝魯西合作才能成功<ref name="ReviewCanby" />。阿诺德认为，艾克洛德与其他演员共同主演时表现最好<ref name="ReviewWapoArnold" />。《华盛顿邮报》还刊登丽塔·肯普利（{{lang|en|Rita Kempley}}）的文章，称艾克洛德与墨菲搭档的效果比起之前与貝魯西也毫不逊色<ref name="ReviewWaPOKempley" />。

《综艺》刊登的评论认为，贝拉米、阿米契、艾略特和柯蒂斯四名配角对电影作用很大<ref name="ReviewVariety" />。影评人称赞柯蒂斯高明的喜剧才华<ref name="ReviewCanby" /><ref name="ReviewWapoArnold" />。阿诺德认为角色本身很老套，情节基本不出预料，但柯蒂斯极富感染力的幽默演出赢得观众认可<ref name="ReviewWapoArnold" />。《人物》周刊称赞她的表演“惊艳”，肯普利觉得她既“婀娜”又“活力四射”<ref name="ReviewWaPOKempley" /><ref name="ReviewPeople" />。坎比声称，柯蒂斯首度主演非喜剧片就表现出“异常出众的幽默细胞”<ref name="ReviewCanby" />。基尔批评兰迪斯总把作品中的女主角描绘成“胸部丰满的兔女郎”，本片也不例外<ref name="ReviewDaveKehr" />。伊伯特认为电影请贝拉米和阿米契出演堪称“神来之笔”<ref name="ReviewEBERT" />；坎比也认为两人的角色无论剧本还是实际刻画都很完善，在他看来，阿米契的角色一直都很幽默，本片也不会让人失望<ref name="ReviewCanby" />。

《人物》周刊赞扬导演内敛和克制的风格，是电影成功的重要原因<ref name="ReviewPeople" />。坎比称，兰迪斯已经证明他既能掌控特效的堆砌，也能驾御戏点精准的喜剧<ref name="ReviewCanby" />。但阿诺德提出异议，觉得导演对本片喜剧时机的把握不及前作，处理素材的能力尚显不足<ref name="ReviewWapoArnold" />。《人物》周刊还称赞两位编剧精心编写的剧本<ref name="ReviewPeople" />，但阿诺德认为他们未能百尺竿头更进一步，像过去的脱线喜剧那样着眼应对社会差异，升华主题<ref name="ReviewWapoArnold" />。

=== 荣誉 ===
