艾略特和柯蒂斯分别获[[第37届英国电影学院奖|第37届英国电影学院奖]][[英國電影學院獎最佳男配角|最佳男配角]]和[[英國電影學院獎最佳女配角|最佳女配角奖]]，哈里斯和魏因格罗德获[[英国电影学院奖最佳原创剧本|最佳原创剧本]]奖提名，但不敌1982年黑色喜剧《[[喜劇之王_(美國1982年電影)|喜剧之王]]》的编剧[[保罗·D·齐默尔曼|保罗·D·齐默尔曼]]（{{lang|en|Paul D. Zimmerman}}）。<ref name="BAFTA37">{{cite web | title = Film Nominations 1983 | url = http://awards.bafta.org/award/1984/film | publisher = [[英国电影和电视艺术学院|British Academy of Film and Television Arts]] | accessdate = 2020-11-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201104164503/http://awards.bafta.org/award/1984/film | archivedate = 2020-11-04 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

== 发行之后 ==

=== 成绩分析和影响 ===
[[File:Eddie_Murphy_by_David_Shankbone.jpg|upright]]》和《颠倒乾坤》的成功令[[艾迪·墨菲|艾迪·墨菲]]一跃成为电影巨星]]

1983年暑期美国电影票房超过15亿美元，正如业界预测的那样超过上年纪录，即便考虑票价上涨因素增幅依然可观<ref name="NYTimesRecordSummer" />。不过，全年电影还是既有黑马，又有出人意料的失利。《超人III》、动作喜剧《[[横冲直撞斗飞车|横冲直撞斗飞车]]》（''{{lang|en|Smokey and the Bandit Part 3}}''）和《[[王牌赛手|王牌赛手]]》（''{{lang|en|Stroker Ace}}''）均未达票房预期，大明星[[史提夫·馬丁|史提夫·馬丁]]主演的科幻喜剧《[[双脑人|双脑人]]》同样表现欠佳<ref name="NYTimesSep181983">{{cite news | first = Vincent | last = Canby | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1983/09/18/movies/film-view-at-the-box-office-summer-has-a-split-personality.html | title = Film View; At The Box Office, Summer Has A Split Personality | date = 1983-09-18 | newspaper = The New York Times | accessdate = 2020-11-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200828115300/https://www.nytimes.com/1983/09/18/movies/film-view-at-the-box-office-summer-has-a-split-personality.html | archivedate = 2020-08-28 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。相比之下，《闪电舞》评价不佳却是全年最大的黑马，冲至年度票房榜第三<ref name="NYTimesRecordSummer" />。《纽约时报》同年九月发文，称年度票房榜前15的电影中只有《颠倒乾坤》值得毫无保留地推荐<ref name="NYTimesSep181983" />。影片既叫好又叫座，商业表现可与《闪电舞》和《绝地归来》一较短长<ref name="TheSpectator">{{cite journal | first = Lindsay | last = Johns | url = https://www.spectator.co.uk/article/trading-places-at-30---one-of-the-funniest-films-of-all-time | title = Trading Places at 30 - one of the funniest films of all time | date = 2013-11-30 | journal = [[旁觀者|The Spectator]] | accessdate = 2020-11-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200919070738/https://www.spectator.co.uk/article/trading-places-at-30---one-of-the-funniest-films-of-all-time | archivedate = 2020-09-19 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref name="NYTimesSep181983" />。时任[[米高梅|米高梅/联艺]]电影制作副总裁[[彼得·巴特|彼得·巴特]]（{{lang|en|Peter Bart}}）声称，《颠倒乾坤》属于卖弄噱头的“[[高概念|高概念]]”电影，情节和人物塑造处于次要地位。他还称，本片和《闪电舞》的成功导致许多人向他推销电影构想，大多混有《颠倒乾坤》式的高概念，结合与《闪电舞》相比换汤不换药的霹雳舞或健身房背景。在他看来，这样的趋势很要不得。<ref name="NYTimesOct101983">{{cite news | first = Aljean | last = Harmetz | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1983/10/10/movies/movies-for-84-will-try-to-copy-successes-of-83.html | title = Movies For '84 Will Try To Copy Successes Of '83 | date = 1983-10-10 | newspaper = The New York Times | accessdate = 2020-11-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200828125412/https://www.nytimes.com/1983/10/10/movies/movies-for-84-will-try-to-copy-successes-of-83.html | archivedate = 2020-08-28 | deadurl = no}}</ref>据哈里斯回忆，曾有人询问本片剧本是否源于制片人[[阿羅·拉索|阿羅·拉索]]或[[杰弗瑞·卡森伯格|杰弗瑞·卡森伯格]]的构想，再聘请他来编写。哈里斯还称，从人们想要分享功劳就能看出，本片肯定很成功。<ref name="BIOralHistory" />

《颠倒乾坤》对片中许多演员的事业影响很大<ref name="BIOralHistory" />，其中墨菲最为显著，凭借一年两部大卖作品，他从电视笑匠华丽转身为超级巨星<ref name="NYTimesMurphyAfter">{{cite news | first = Richard | last = Grenier | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1985/03/10/arts/eddie-murphy-s-comic-touch.html | title = Eddie Murphy's Comic Touch | date = 1985-03-10 | newspaper = The New York Times | accessdate = 2020-11-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200704094312/https://www.nytimes.com/1985/03/10/arts/eddie-murphy-s-comic-touch.html | archivedate = 2020-07-04 | deadurl = no | page = 21}}</ref>。业内专业人士认为他的票房号召力仅次于[[克林·伊斯威特|克林特·伊斯特伍德]]，此前任何非裔美国演员都难望项背<ref name="NYTimesMurphyAfter" />。据称他主演《颠倒乾坤》的片酬达100万美元，获邀主演第三部电影《[[比佛利山警探|比佛利山警探]]》时要价300万美元，这已是当时最热门电影明星的薪酬水平<ref name="WashingtonPost1Million" />。

《颠倒乾坤》上映后不久，派拉蒙影业和墨菲签署价值2500万美元的五部电影独家合约，数额之高当时还非常罕见。派拉蒙还同意为他开办的艾迪·墨菲影业注资<ref name="WashingtonPost1Million" /><ref name="NYTimesApril301984">{{cite news | first = Robert | last = Palmer | page = C11 | archivedate = 2020-08-28 | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1984/04/30/arts/eddie-murphy-as-pop-singer.html | title = Eddie Murphy As Pop Singer | date = 1984-04-30 | newspaper = The New York Times | accessdate = 2020-11-13 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200828170558/https://www.nytimes.com/1984/04/30/arts/eddie-murphy-as-pop-singer.html}}</ref>。除墨菲外，同年涌现的青年明星包括[[馬修·波特歷|馬修·波特歷]]、[[湯姆·克魯斯|湯姆·克魯斯]]和[[米高·基頓|米高·基頓]]，每人都不到30岁，表明观众平均年龄持续增长，从少年成长为青年，电影的主要目标观众不再是儿童<ref name="NYTimesOct101983" />。墨菲迅速成名后离开《周六夜现场》，自称发达引来妒恨，导致他不想再保留这份工作<ref name="RollingStoneMurphy" />。

艾克洛德的事业经历一系列失败后终于从《颠倒乾坤》迎来转机<ref name="NYTimesJune251983">{{cite news | first = Aljean | last = Harmetz | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1983/06/25/movies/film-studios-wonder-if-new-hits-will-last.html | title = Film Studios Wonder If New Hits Will Last | date = 1983-06-25 | newspaper = The New York Times | accessdate = 2020-11-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201108015912/https://www.nytimes.com/1983/06/25/movies/film-studios-wonder-if-new-hits-will-last.html | archivedate = 2020-11-08 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。接下来他在20世纪80年代主演多部成功作品，如1984年的现象级大片《[[魔鬼剋星|魔鬼剋星]]》<ref name="VanityFair2014">{{cite journal | first = Lesley M. M. | last = Blume | journal = [[名利场_(杂志)|Vanity Fair]] | url = https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2014/06/ghostbusters-making-of | title = The Making of ''Ghostbusters'': How Dan Aykroyd, Harold Ramis, and "The Murricane" Built "The Perfect Comedy" | date = 2014-06-04 | accessdate = 2020-11-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201108133835/http://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2014/06/ghostbusters-making-of | archivedate = 2020-11-13 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，1985年的《[[光棍出差|光棍出差]]》（''{{lang|en|Spies Like Us}}''）和1987年的《[[警網_(電影)|法网]]》，1989年的《[[为黛茜小姐开车|为黛茜小姐开车]]》为他赢得[[奥斯卡最佳男配角奖|奥斯卡最佳男配角奖]]提名<ref name="AykroydFandango">{{cite web | url = https://www.fandango.com/people/dan-aykroyd-25896/biography | title = Dan Aykroyd Biography | website = [[Fandango_(公司)|Fandango]] | accessdate = 2020-11-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200809170536/https://www.fandango.com/people/dan-aykroyd-25896/biography | archivedate = 2020-08-09 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref name="AykroydFilmography">{{cite web | url = https://www.fandango.com/people/dan-aykroyd-25896/film-credits | title = Dan Aykroyd Filmography | website = Fandango | accessdate = 2020-11-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200809141005/https://www.fandango.com/people/dan-aykroyd-25896/film-credits | archivedate = 2020-08-09 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。《颠倒乾坤》为柯蒂斯的事业带来突破，不再局限于恐怖片领域。1988年[[约翰·克里斯|约翰·克里斯]]邀请她出演喜剧片《[[一条叫旺达的鱼|一条叫旺达的鱼]]》，根本原因就是看重柯蒂斯在《颠倒乾坤》的演出。<ref name="BIOralHistory" /><ref name="PeopleCurtis" /><ref name="BBCCurtis">{{cite news | first = Almar | last = Haflidason | title = A Fish Called Wanda Special Edition DVD (1988) | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/films/2002/12/23/a_fish_called_wanda_1988_dvd_se_review.shtml | website = [[BBC在線|BBC Online]] | date = 2003 | accessdate = 2020-11-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201030043053/http://www.bbc.co.uk/films/2002/12/23/a_fish_called_wanda_1988_dvd_se_review.shtml | archivedate = 2020-10-30 | deadurl = no}}</ref>柯蒂斯称，兰迪斯当年选择她出演奥菲莉亚可谓“以一己之力改变我的人生”<ref name="BIOralHistory" />。息影十余年的阿米契也凭本片重新回到公众视野，1985年又出演科幻喜剧《[[魔茧|魔茧]]》（''{{lang|en|Cocoon}}''），为他赢得生命中唯一的奥斯卡奖（最佳男配角）<ref name="BIOralHistory" /><ref name="ChicagoTribuneAmechePay" />。

与几位演员相比，导演兰迪斯此后的运气要差得多。他导演《阴阳魔界》期间片场[[阴阳魔界电影拍摄事故|发生重大事故导致多名演员死亡]]，法律诉讼紧随其后，事业遭受挫折，随后导演的几部电影成绩一般。<ref name="RollingStoneMurphyLandis">{{cite journal | first = Bill | last = Zehme | archivedate = 2020-10-29 | url = https://www.rollingstone.com/culture/culture-news/eddie-murphy-call-him-money-82359/ | title = Eddie Murphy: Call Him Money | date = 1989-08-24 | journal = Rolling Stone | accessdate = 2020-11-13 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201029043719/https://www.rollingstone.com/culture/culture-news/eddie-murphy-call-him-money-82359/}}</ref><ref name="LATimesTwilight">{{cite news | first1 = Marc | last1 = Green | first2 = Stephen | last2 = Farber | title = Trapped in the Twilight Zone : A Year After the Trial, Six Years After the Tragedy, the Participants Have Been Touched in Surprisingly Different Ways. And the Hollywood Controversy Still Burns. | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1988-08-28-tm-1446-story.html | newspaper = [[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]] | date = 1988-08-28 | accessdate = 2020-11-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201002022927/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1988-08-28-tm-1446-story.html | archivedate = 2020-10-02 | deadurl = no}}</ref>据墨菲透露，邀请兰迪斯导演1988年喜剧片《美国之旅》（''{{lang|en|Coming to America}}''）就是为支持他的事业。两人在片场的相处不甚和睦，但之后又在1994年的《[[比佛利山超级警探3|比佛利山超级警探3]]》（''{{lang|en|Beverly Hills Cop III}}''）第三度合作。<ref name="EmpireRetrospective" /><ref name="RollingStoneMurphyLandis" /><ref name="WAPOCollabs">{{cite news | archivedate = 2020-11-05 | url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/15-moments-that-define-the-career-of-eddie-murphy/2015/10/13/e02069e2-706f-11e5-9cbb-790369643cf9_gallery.html | title = 15 moments that define the career of Eddie Murphy | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201105131020/https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/15-moments-that-define-the-career-of-eddie-murphy/2015/10/13/e02069e2-706f-11e5-9cbb-790369643cf9_gallery.html | newspaper = The Washington Post | accessdate = 2020-11-13 | deadurl = no}}</ref>哈里斯和魏因格罗德跻身大牌编剧行列<ref name="BIOralHistory" />，两人后来起诉《颠倒乾坤》制片人阿羅·拉索没有按约定支付0.5%的制片人利润分成，估计价值15万美元，案件结果至今不明<ref name="AFI" />。

=== 家用媒体 ===
20世纪80年代初，[[錄影機|錄影機]]家用视频市场迅速普及。1982年时，[[家用录像系统|VHS]]录像带营收尚不入片商法眼，但1983年局面大变，录像带收入最高可达电影总收益的13%，单北美洲录像带版权收入就有50万美元。<ref name="NYTimesHomeMedia">{{cite news | first = Aljean | last = Harmetz | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1984/05/07/movies/hollywood-thriving-on-video-cassette-boom.html | title = Hollywood Thriving On Video-cassette Boom | date = 1984-05-17 | newspaper = The New York Times | accessdate = 2020-11-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201027034941/https://www.nytimes.com/1984/05/07/movies/hollywood-thriving-on-video-cassette-boom.html | archivedate = 2020-10-27 | deadurl = no}}</ref>派拉蒙于1984年5月发行《颠倒乾坤》的{{lang|en|VHS}}录像带，单价39.95美元<ref name="NYTimesMay1984">{{cite news | archivedate = 2020-07-05 | deadurl = no | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1984/05/27/arts/in-brief-recent-films-on-cassettes-209161.html | title = In Brief: Recent Films On Cassettes | date = 1984-05-27 | newspaper = The New York Times | accessdate = 2020-11-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200705221248/https://www.nytimes.com/1984/05/27/arts/in-brief-recent-films-on-cassettes-209161.html | page = 224}}</ref>，远低于80美元的市场标准价，推动家用录像机普及。按此时的市场惯例，票房大卖电影预计能在家用媒体市场拿下五百至一千万美元<ref name="NYTimesHomeMedia" />，本片及动作惊悚片《[[撥雲見日|拨云见日]]》在五月的录像带租赁市场表现出众<ref name="NYTimesHomeMedia" />。派拉蒙与[[Showtime電視網|Showtime電視網]]签署价格五亿美元的独家协议，在该台播出旗下包括《颠倒乾坤》在内的众多电影，有评论称派拉蒙认为{{lang|en|HBO}}在电视电影播放市场一家独大的地位对片商营收不利，故而有意打破垄断<ref name="NYTimesHomeMedia" /><ref name="NYTimesHBOSHowTime">{{cite news | first = David | last = Hadju | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1984/01/08/movies/cable-s-showtime-buys-film-package.html | title = Film View; After A Slow Beginning, A Rousing Conclusion | date = 1984-01-08 | newspaper = The New York Times | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200828160033/https://www.nytimes.com/1984/01/08/movies/cable-s-showtime-buys-film-package.html | archivedate = 2020-08-28 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-11-13 | page = 226}}</ref>。

