片中情节跨度是圣诞节前后几个星期，但这不影响媒体将《颠倒乾坤》视为圣诞电影<ref name="TheAtlanticXmas" /><ref name="DOGXmas" />。2008年，《[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]》宣称本片作为圣诞电影杰作，还远远没有得到应有的待遇<ref name="WAPOUnderrated">{{cite news | url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/express/wp/2008/12/17/the_most_underrated_xmas_flick/ | title = Holiday 5: The Most Underrated Christmas Flicks | date = 2008-12-17 | newspaper = The Washington Post | accessdate = 2020-11-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200911062209/https://www.washingtonpost.com/express/wp/2008/12/17/the_most_underrated_xmas_flick/ | archivedate = 2020-09-11 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。《[[大西洋_(雜誌)|大西洋]]》杂志认为本片是不那么传统的圣诞电影，但主题仍与圣诞节紧密相关，特别是涉及贫富鸿沟的部分<ref name="TheAtlanticXmas" />。影片登上众多媒体评选的最佳圣诞电影榜，如《帝国杂志》排名第五<ref name="XmasEmpire">{{cite journal | first = Helen | last = O'Hara | date = 2016-12-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200731001025/https://www.empireonline.com/movies/features/empire-30-best-christmas-movies/ | url = https://www.empireonline.com/movies/features/empire-30-best-christmas-movies/ | title = The 30 Best Christmas Movies | journal = Empire | accessdate = 2020-11-13 | archivedate = 2020-07-31 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》排第12<ref name="XmasEW">{{cite journal | first = Chris | title = These are the top 20 Christmas movies ever | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201030025132/https://ew.com/movies/20-top-christmas-movies-ever/ | url = https://ew.com/movies/20-top-christmas-movies-ever/ | journal = [[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]] | last = Nashawaty | date = 2018-11-13 | accessdate = 2020-11-13 | archivedate = 2020-10-30 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，“[[惊悚网|惊悚网]]”（{{lang|en|Thrillist}}）第13<ref name="XmasThrillist">{{cite web | first1 = Dan | last1 = Jackson | first2 = Matt | last2 = Patches | title = The 50 Best Christmas Movies of All Time | archivedate = 2020-11-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201109162110/https://www.thrillist.com/entertainment/nation/best-christmas-movies-of-all-time | url = https://www.thrillist.com/entertainment/nation/best-christmas-movies-of-all-time | website = Thrillist | date = 2019-11-26 | accessdate = 2020-11-13 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，《Time Out》第23<ref name="XmasTimeOut">{{cite journal | title = The 50 best Christmas movies | url = https://www.timeout.com/london/film/the-50-best-christmas-movies | journal = [[Time_Out|Time Out]] | date = 2019-10-22 | accessdate = 2020-11-13 | archivedate = 2020-11-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201103144546/https://www.timeout.com/london/film/the-50-best-christmas-movies | deadurl = no}}</ref>，烂番茄第24<ref name="LastingRTXmas" />，《[[今天_(NBC)|今天]]》第45<ref name="XmasToday">{{cite web | title = Here are the 75 best Christmas movies of all time for the holidays | url = https://www.today.com/popculture/75-best-christmas-movies-all-time-2019-holidays-ranked-t168135 | work = [[今天_(NBC)|Today]] | date = 2019-11-28 | accessdate = 2020-11-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200510193818/https://www.today.com/popculture/75-best-christmas-movies-all-time-2019-holidays-ranked-t168135 | archivedate = 2020-05-10 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，《乡村生活》（''{{lang|en|Country Living}}''）和《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》列入但未排名<ref name="XmasCountry">{{cite journal | first = Taysha | last = Murtaugh | url = https://www.countryliving.com/life/entertainment/g5034/top-christmas-movies/?slide=37 | title = 71 Best Christmas Movies to Binge-Watch This Holiday Season | journal = Country Living | date = 2020-10-10 | accessdate = 2020-11-13}}</ref><ref name="XmasTelegraph">{{cite news | title = The 25 best Christmas movies, from Love Actually to The Muppets Christmas Carol | archivedate = 2019-12-26 | deadurl = no | url = https://www.telegraph.co.uk/films/0/best-christmas-movies-watch-top-films-elf-home-alone-die-hard/trading/ | newspaper = [[每日电讯报|The Daily Telegraph]] | date = 2019-12-24 | accessdate = 2020-11-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191226055030/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/films/0/best-christmas-movies-watch-top-films-elf-home-alone-die-hard/trading/}}</ref>。1984年在意大利上映后，本片就一直是该国电视上颇得观众青睐的圣诞电影<ref name="XmasItaly">{{Cite web | first = Alessandro | last = Beretta | title = Perché a ogni vigilia di Natale c'è "Una poltrona per due" su Italia 1 | url = https://www.corriere.it/spettacoli/cards/poltrona-due-cinque-cose-che-non-sapete-film-che-mediaset-vi-propone-29-anni/da-29-anni-film-mediaset-feste.shtml | newspaper = [[晚邮报|Corriere della Sera]] | date = 2018-12-24 | accessdate = 2020-11-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200809164207/https://www.corriere.it/spettacoli/cards/poltrona-due-cinque-cose-che-non-sapete-film-che-mediaset-vi-propone-29-anni/da-29-anni-film-mediaset-feste.shtml | archivedate = 2020-08-09 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

根据烂番茄网站收集的46篇评论，《颠倒乾坤》“新鲜度”达87%，平均评分7.45（最高10分）。网站的共识评述写道：“《颠倒乾坤》包含艾迪·墨菲与丹·艾克洛德的巧妙互动，是引人入注的社会讽刺佳作。”<ref name="RottenTomatoes">{{cite web | url = https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/trading_places | title = Trading Places (1983) | website = [[爛番茄|Rotten Tomatoes]] | accessdate = 2020-11-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200930062324/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/trading_places | archivedate = 2020-09-30 | deadurl = no}}</ref>{{lang|en|[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]}}根据十篇评论打出69分，代表“普遍好评”<ref name="Metacritic">{{cite web | url = https://www.metacritic.com/movie/trading-places | title = Trading Places | website = [[Metacritic|Metacritic]] | accessdate = 2020-11-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200918235502/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/trading-places | archivedate = 2020-09-18 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

随着时间的推移，部分评论家在称赞电影部分元素能够经受时间考验的同时，也指出片中存在一些今日眼光来看问题多多的内容，如种族主义言辞、黑脸扮装，以及暗示比克斯遭大猩猩强奸<ref name="TheAtlanticXmas" /><ref name="GuardianApril2014" /><ref name="NYTIMESRacial">{{cite news | first = Sharon | last = Waxman | title = Using a Racial Epithet To Combat Racism | url = https://www.nytimes.com/2004/07/03/arts/using-a-racial-epithet-to-combat-racism.html | newspaper = The New York Times | date = 2004-07-03 | accessdate = 2020-11-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201109004247/https://www.nytimes.com/2004/07/03/arts/using-a-racial-epithet-to-combat-racism.html | archivedate = 2020-11-09 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref name="RacialGQ">{{cite journal | first = Alfred | last = Tong | title = Dan Aykroyd's Trading Places watch is worth much more than $50 | url = https://www.gq-magazine.co.uk/fashion/article/trading-places-rochefoucauld-world-complication | journal = [[GQ|GQ]] | date = 2020-06-12 | accessdate = 2020-11-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200718111618/https://www.gq-magazine.co.uk/fashion/article/trading-places-rochefoucauld-world-complication | archivedate = 2020-07-18 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。片中莫蒂默称永远不会容许“黑鬼”经营他的企业，影片在电视上播映时有时会把这个词消音甚至把整段掐掉。2004年纪录片《N开头那个词》（''{{lang|en|The N-Word}}''）的导演托德·威廉姆斯（{{lang|en|Todd Williams}}）认为，这段台词对电影非常重要，不该遭审查删除。在他看来，这种假装某个词不存在的做法非常危险，就像有些人可能会故意对某些不好的事视而不见。<ref name="NYTIMESRacial" />《[[GQ|GQ]]》也有类似看法，觉得这些“敏感词”不致影响电影的社会意义<ref name="RacialGQ" />。2020年[[乔治·弗洛伊德之死引发的示威活动|乔治·弗洛伊德之死引发大量抗议示威]]，[[天空英国|天空英国]]广播公司播放《颠倒乾坤》等16部电影时加入如下免责声明：“本片的部分态度、言辞和文化描述已经过时，如今可能引起反感”<ref name="VarietySKY">{{cite journal | first = Manori | last = Ravindran | title = Sky Adds 'Outdated Attitudes' Disclaimer for 'Jungle Book,' 'Breakfast at Tiffany's' | date = 2020-06-21 | url = https://variety.com/2020/film/global/sky-disclaimer-jungle-book-breakfast-at-tiffanys-flash-gordon-goonies-1234643825/ | journal = Variety | accessdate = 2020-11-14 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201008011546/https://variety.com/2020/film/global/sky-disclaimer-jungle-book-breakfast-at-tiffanys-flash-gordon-goonies-1234643825/ | archivedate = 2020-10-08 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

